statements: SELECT * FROM StockPortfolioOptimization;
SELECT stock_symbol, date, historical_price FROM StockPortfolioOptimization;
SELECT id, stock_symbol FROM StockPortfolioOptimization WHERE ai_algorithm_used='Machine Learning';
SELECT stock_symbol, historical_price FROM StockPortfolioOptimization WHERE date='2022-01-15';
SELECT * FROM StockPortfolioOptimization ORDER BY date DESC;
SELECT * FROM StockPortfolioOptimization WHERE stock_symbol = 'AAPL' ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 10
SELECT MIN(historical_price) AS min_price, MAX(historical_price) AS max_price FROM StockPortfolioOptimization
SELECT stock_symbol, AVG(historical_price) AS avg_price FROM StockPortfolioOptimization GROUP BY stock_symbol HAVING COUNT(*) > 5 ORDER BY avg_price DESC
SELECT date, COUNT(*) AS total_records FROM StockPortfolioOptimization GROUP BY date HAVING total_records > 1
SELECT * FROM StockPortfolioOptimization WHERE ai_algorithm_used = 'Machine Learning' OR ai_algorithm_used = 'Technical Analysis' ORDER BY id ASC
SELECT * FROM stock_data
SELECT stock_name, stock_price FROM stock_data WHERE volume > 10000
SELECT stock_id, stock_name, market_cap FROM stock_data ORDER BY market_cap DESC
SELECT stock_name, volume FROM stock_data WHERE stock_price < 50 ORDER BY volume ASC
SELECT stock_id, stock_name, timestamp FROM stock_data WHERE stock_price BETWEEN 100 AND 200
SELECT stock_name, stock_price FROM stock_data WHERE stock_price > 100 ORDER BY stock_price DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT stock_id, stock_name, market_cap FROM stock_data WHERE volume > 100000 ORDER BY market_cap DESC;
SELECT * FROM stock_data WHERE volume < 5000 AND market_cap > 100000000 ORDER BY volume ASC, market_cap DESC;
SELECT s.stock_name, r.recommendation, r.confidence_score FROM stock_data s INNER JOIN stock_recommendations r ON s.stock_id = r.stock_id WHERE r.recommendation_date = '2022-01-15';
SELECT stock_id, SUM(stock_price) AS total_price FROM stock_data GROUP BY stock_id HAVING SUM(stock_price) > 50000 ORDER BY total_price DESC;
SELECT * FROM stock_portfolio;
SELECT stock_name, purchase_price FROM stock_portfolio ORDER BY stock_id DESC;
SELECT stock_id, stock_name, purchase_price, purchase_date FROM stock_portfolio WHERE purchase_date >= '2022-01-01' AND purchase_date <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT SUM(purchase_price) AS total_purchase_price FROM stock_portfolio;
SELECT stock_id, MAX(purchase_price) AS max_purchase_price FROM stock_portfolio GROUP BY stock_id;
SELECT stock_name, purchase_price FROM stock_portfolio WHERE stock_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM historical_market_data WHERE market_date > '2021-01-01' ORDER BY close_price DESC;
SELECT stock_name, purchase_price, purchase_date FROM stock_portfolio JOIN optimization_results ON stock_portfolio.stock_id = optimization_results.stock_id;
SELECT stock_name, purchase_price FROM stock_portfolio WHERE purchase_price > 100 ORDER BY purchase_date ASC;
SELECT stock_name, close_price, volume FROM stock_portfolio JOIN historical_market_data ON stock_portfolio.stock_id = historical_market_data.stock_id WHERE market_date = '2021-06-30';
SELECT * FROM StockPrices ORDER BY date DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT stock_symbol, open_price, close_price FROM StockPrices WHERE stock_symbol='AAPL';
SELECT stock_symbol, date, high_price, low_price FROM StockPrices WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-01-31';
SELECT id, stock_symbol, date, dividend_yield FROM StockMetrics WHERE dividend_yield > 2.5;
SELECT portfolio_id, sum(current_value) AS total_value FROM PortfolioHoldings GROUP BY portfolio_id ORDER BY total_value DESC;
SELECT * FROM StockPrices ORDER BY date DESC, open_price ASC LIMIT 10;
SELECT stock_symbol, date, close_price FROM StockPrices WHERE close_price > 100 ORDER BY close_price DESC;
SELECT AVG(open_price) AS avg_open_price, AVG(close_price) AS avg_close_price FROM StockPrices WHERE date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-02-28';
SELECT stock_symbol, MAX(high_price) AS highest_price FROM StockPrices GROUP BY stock_symbol ORDER BY highest_price DESC;

SELECT sh.stock_symbol, COUNT(ph.stock_symbol) AS holdings_count FROM StockMetrics sm JOIN PortfolioHoldings ph ON sm.stock_symbol = ph.stock_symbol JOIN StockPrices sp ON sm.stock_symbol = sp.stock_symbol GROUP BY sh.stock_symbol HAVING COUNT(ph.stock_symbol) > 5 ORDER BY holdings_count DESC;
SELECT * FROM stock_prices;
SELECT stock_symbol, price FROM stock_transactions WHERE transaction_type='Buy';
SELECT model_name, model_type FROM ai_models ORDER BY model_name DESC;
SELECT stock_symbol, SUM(quantity) AS total_quantity FROM portfolio_holdings GROUP BY stock_symbol;
SELECT * FROM optimization_results WHERE performance_score > 0.75;
SELECT * FROM stock_prices ORDER BY date DESC, price ASC LIMIT 10
SELECT stock_symbol, price, date FROM stock_transactions WHERE quantity > 100 AND transaction_type = 'BUY' ORDER BY price DESC
SELECT id, model_name, model_type, description FROM ai_models WHERE model_type = 'Regression'
SELECT * FROM portfolio_holdings WHERE quantity >= 500 ORDER BY purchase_date ASC LIMIT 5
SELECT portfolio_id, performance_score, optimization_details FROM optimization_results WHERE optimization_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' ORDER BY performance_score DESC
